#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:12
msgid "Traffic management"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:14
msgid ""
"**Added** `automatic protocol determination </docs/ops/configuration"
"/traffic-management/protocol-selection/>`_ of HTTP or TCP for outbound "
"traffic when ports are not named according to Istio’s `conventions "
"</docs/ops/deployment/requirements/>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:19
msgid "**Added** a mode to the Gateway API for mutual TLS operation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:20
msgid ""
"**Fixed** issues present when a service communicates over the network "
"first in permissive mutual TLS mode for protocols like MySQL and MongoDB."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Improved** Envoy proxy readiness checks. They now check Envoy’s "
"readiness status."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:25
msgid ""
"**Improved** container ports are no longer required in the pod spec. All "
"ports are `captured by default </faq/traffic-management/#controlling-"
"inbound-ports>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:28
msgid ""
"**Improved** the ``EnvoyFilter`` API. You can now add or update all "
"configurations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:30
msgid ""
"**Improved** the Redis load balancer to now default to `MAGLEV "
"<https://www.envoyproxy.io/docs/envoy/v1.6.0/intro/arch_overview/load_balancing#maglev>`_"
" when using the Redis proxy."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:33
msgid ""
"**Improved** load balancing to direct traffic to the `same region and "
"zone </faq/traffic-management/#controlling-inbound-ports>`_ by default."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:36
#, python-format
msgid ""
"**Improved** Pilot by reducing CPU utilization. The reduction approaches "
"90% depending on the specific deployment."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:38
msgid ""
"**Improved** the ``ServiceEntry`` API to allow for the same hostname in "
"different namespaces."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3/change-notes/index.rst:40
msgid ""
"**Improved** the `Sidecar API "
"</docs/reference/config/networking/sidecar/#OutboundTrafficPolicy>`_ to "
"customize the ``OutboundTrafficPolicy`` policy."
msgstr ""

